<div class="prose">
  <p>Simulators in this course aren't games — they're research instruments. Each scenario is modeled on real geology and real history. The data your simulation runs produce (placements, budget, population saved, score) become the iteration evidence in your unit portfolios. Treat them seriously, predict before you run, reflect after, and document like you would any other AI-assisted work.</p>
</div>

